data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled on a sprawling 16-acre lot. This barn-style property offers a unique blend of rustic charm and modern comforts. With its spacious layout, and beautiful surroundings, this home is sure to impress.  This property offers you an extra-large family room, perfect for entertaining. The room's generous size provides ample space for various seating arrangements and activities. Natural light fills the room through large windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  The property features 3 bedrooms,3 bathrooms. The master bedroom is truly a retreat, designed in an apartment style with its own kitchen and en-suite bathroom. This thoughtful layout provides privacy and convenience.  Step outside to you screened porch an excellent spot to relax and enjoy the tranquil surroundings. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a summer barbecue, this versatile space allows you to savor the beauty of nature while remaining protected from the elements.   Additionally, the property boasts a storage shed, spacious garage/workshop.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this unique property your own!
